rComments: Well organized but he needs to work on his teaching style.  Very boring and sometimes bordering on arrogant.  Class was pretty easy so I wouldn't go out of my way to take another one of his classes.
nerdy and boring but a breezy class.

Professor Bernstein is a gem! He is organized, helpful and passionate about intnl rel. He is painstaking and extreme clear. He only teaches p. 1 of the course so you get used to his caring and then the 2nd sem prof is a huge let down! Nice guy, def would take another course with him!
Very boring lectures but he's so sweet and kind of funny.
HE is the MOST organized prof in the history of UTM. He supplies all the slides you'll ever need, and knows exactly what he's doingg! Taking his course was a pleasure!
Great professor! however, be prepared to work your butt off~
I thought this course was going to be easy, but I was wrong. It's probably my lowest mark, however the prof supplies really good lecture slides, but is a tough marker.
ehh he's okaay.. nothing that GREAT!! his TA is a tough grader.. grrr!! His lecture slides are very very good though..

The best prof ever!!! I got a poli sci. minor after taking his class as a breadth requirement.  If you want to get your money's worth taking a class, this one is it.  I've never wanted to attend class more than this one.  I would take anything he teaches.
